{
  "stem": "23131.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said to him, you know, they're all learning the-- the Bible of the communism and the-- the Marxism and all that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he couldn't-- you know, I can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, he says.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have all kind of groups, that each one is learning something else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so today, they-- all the people have nothing to do so they are learning the story of the communists.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he believed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But was a time, I-- I-- it's very-- if it's important, I'll find out, it's-- because I have somebody to find out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he-- there were seven people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His five daughters are still in Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew when it's Pesach.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could-- we knew-- we baked matzohs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] But they-- this group from the-- this-- they baked matzohs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They marked it, the holidays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Listen, we couldn't do these things because we didn't know when we had to run.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't that I'm sitting in the house and if it's raining I don't-- there was nowhere I-- they didn't-- no rain, and no snow, and no wind, and no nothing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You want to survive, so you go against everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You run, you go, you-- you fall, you get up, you go again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Me?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm a, by nature, a pessimist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what they say, or-- I don't feel like this, but that's what they all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But Tuvia always was optimistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not everybody, but some of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cliques?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were cliques.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One city didn't bother with the other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, everybody-- you must understand now that everybody was afraid, so much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wanted so much to survive, that they thought, if another person-- there were plenty of people that were against it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came, the first ones to the woods.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
